Michel Ancel, celebrated creator of Rayman, Beyond Good & Evil and the Raving Rabbids returns to his roots to bring us Rayman Origins, an adventure platformer HD, 2D and horizontal scrolling co-op with 4 players. Play Rayman Origins and discover or rediscover the magical universe and legendary 2D gameplay that captured the hearts of millions of fans. When the Glade of Dreams is overrun by dark toons wicked, the Council of the Fairies invoked quickly Rayman to save the situation but the hero of light is not alone. Rayman will team up with his friend Globox and two wizards called Tiny somewhat crazy. Together they form the most bizarre and fun team of heroes the world has ever known and in your hands is to restore peace to the Glade of Dreams ... or watch their beloved home vanishes into a horrible nightmare.
